Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.53,0:00:02.37,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur10}那么… 还不如…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.18,0:00:04.38,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur10}我亲手…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.18,0:00:05.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  佳乃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:08.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.80,0:00:24.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃！ 佳乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.67,0:02:04.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这伤痕恐怕要留下一段时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.30,0:02:06.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}给你们添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.55,0:02:09.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}对不起  国崎  神尾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.17,0:02:11.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  不…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.29,0:02:13.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我们倒是没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.48,0:02:23.61,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那是佳乃小时候的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:27.60,AIR Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,770)}羽   毛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.63,0:02:31.09,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我们的母亲去世后的第一个夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.87,0:02:41.32,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看啊看啊  姐姐  是气球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:44.79,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那边那边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.98,0:02:47.46,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}买了那个的话  是不是就能飞上天空了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:50.21,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}要是一个气球就能把人带上天的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:52.60,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那个摊子不早就飞上天了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:54.59,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哦… 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.85,0:02:56.63,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}姐姐真聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.83,0:03:00.56,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但那就是说  只要有很多气球就可以飞起来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:03.53,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯… 大概能吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:09.50,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不过  只能买一个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.24,0:03:14.53,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就算只有一个  只要把它吹得很大就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.60,0:03:18.19,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那样的话  就算再重的东西也可以带起来了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:20.94,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那样一来可就买不了别的东西了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.64,0:03:22.13,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:27.28,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}给你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.44,0:03:29.44,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇  谢谢姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:35.46,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}佳乃一直想飞到天上去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:38.42,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因为她相信那样就可以见到母亲了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:44.89,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我告诉过她  妈妈在天上注视着佳乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:48.78,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}父亲和我都不忍告诉她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.61,0:03:52.18,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}妈妈已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.73,0:04:02.44,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}佳乃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:47.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}接下来  发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:50.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什么也没有发生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:54.46,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是谁在这里胡闹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.63,0:04:58.61,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}于是我们把羽毛放回原处  回家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:12.58,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我已经去不了妈妈那里了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.23,0:05:15.84,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}从第二天开始  佳乃就变得有些异常了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.49,0:05:18.07,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有时会害怕强光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:21.07,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有时会不知不觉地走到外边去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.56,0:05:24.48,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}而且有时还会嘟囔一些莫名其妙的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:29.31,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有一天夜晚  我醒来时发现佳乃不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:30.79,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我慌忙去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:34.27,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}才发现她在这间诊疗室里用手术刀割伤了自己的手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:38.14,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好在处理及时  才没有大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:42.34,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那时候我就想  这不是佳乃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:45.16,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}而是其他什么人在扮演着佳乃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:49.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就是所谓的多重人格吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:51.50,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也许吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:54.67,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这是一条神奇的缎带
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.21,0:05:56.87,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只要一直把它戴到长大为止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:05:58.49,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你就可以使用魔法了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:06:01.33,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以  无论碰到什么事都不要把它解开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:08.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是这样啊  送给佳乃缎带的原来是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:11.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在她失去理智想要割伤手腕的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:13.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看到这条缎带就会找回自我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:15.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我小时候这样想来着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:19.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}佳乃也并不记得多少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.74,0:06:22.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}从一开始就不存在什么魔法的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:26.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我那时候下定决心要继承父亲的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:31.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因为我认为  成为医生就可以治好佳乃的病了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:34.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}佳乃碰过的那根羽毛到底是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:35.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.17,0:06:39.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好像是从很久以前就被供奉在那所神社里的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:41.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但管理人也并不知道更多的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:44.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}会不会是那根羽毛的诅咒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.03,0:06:49.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}作为医生是不能认同这种理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:54.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不过那有可能是诱发心病的契机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:58.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那个时候的佳乃刚刚失去母亲  心理压力很大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.17,0:07:01.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想这才应该是根本的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:05.71,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今天也要去雾岛那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:07.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  而且还有零工要做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:10.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我过一会儿也想去看看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:11.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:14.26,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}交到新朋友不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:17.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}昨晚  我又做梦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:20.22,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是一个在天空中飞翔的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:24.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}自从那之后  我就在梦中渐渐地追溯着时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:31.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在昨晚的梦中  我在天空中很悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.74,0:07:32.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}悲伤？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:38.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我像从前一样在天上飞翔着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:42.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}而且我在那里感到很悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.99,0:07:47.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在那么清爽的微风中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:52.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}为什么我还会那样悲伤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:53.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那不是梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:55.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}与你无关的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.77,0:07:57.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:08:00.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你要是不笑的话就会连我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:01.22,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.72,0:08:03.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以  你还是笑一笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:06.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}V
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:17.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什么也没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.07,0:08:18.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊～！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:20.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}找到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,0:08:24.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你在搞什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:28.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇！ 国崎往人？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:31.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你怎么会来这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:32.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我还想问你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:35.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你捡那种玩意  难不成在搞废品回收吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:36.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真烦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.89,0:08:39.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我的兴趣就是在这种地方捡东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:42.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真是世上最无聊的兴趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:43.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你少管
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:50.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真羡慕你啊  每天只是玩就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:53.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}国崎往人还不是和我差不多嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.29,0:08:56.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我可是要干活的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:59.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今天也正要去工作的地方干活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:01.22,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:03.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯？ 上厕所吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:06.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不是  看那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.54,0:09:13.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:19.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那莫非就是远野的母亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:21.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:25.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.69,0:09:37.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}美风  看上去很寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:39.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呐  向美风打个招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:41.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想她一个人一定会很寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:44.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊  我去打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:46.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}远野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.31,0:09:58.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}国崎先生在这里做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.35,0:10:02.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  和小满一起散步来着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:03.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哦…  哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:05.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那家伙去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.01,0:10:08.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}和小满在一起的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:10.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  刚才的确是在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.50,0:10:16.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}关于刚才和我在一起的那个人  小满说过什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.94,0:10:19.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什么也没说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:22.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是吗  那就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.50,0:10:24.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那个人是你的母亲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.90,0:10:25.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:29.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我从前帮她搬过东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:33.03,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}说起来  你们俩给人的感觉的确很像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:37.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我对那个人来说  是梦的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:38.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:47.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}别逃啊  土豆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.67,0:10:49.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}来  让你凉快凉快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.73,0:10:56.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}挺有精神的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.48,0:10:59.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  往人  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:02.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}对不起  昨晚又给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.82,0:11:04.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}没什么大不了的  别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:06.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哦  你来了  国崎君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今天也有很多工作要做哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:23.77,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}佳乃还在睡午觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:27.43,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  考虑到昨晚的事  我让她休息去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:29.39,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也该起来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:31.18,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:32.71,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}佳乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.58,0:11:35.11,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.66,0:11:45.27,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想往人会相信我的  所以才写了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:48.23,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我还是决定到天上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:52.34,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那样的话  我想大家就都会幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:56.26,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}感觉也会碰到往人正在寻找的那个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.93,0:11:58.67,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}虽然不知道是什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:12:00.94,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但我一定会把她带来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:04.83,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在那之前  希望你能照看我的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:08.27,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}其实  姐姐很勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.17,0:12:12.77,AIR context 4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}另外  脖子的伤真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:34.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}佳乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:41.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}振作点  佳乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.60,0:12:44.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}没有外伤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:46.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那这血是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.08,0:12:50.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}没有出血的迹象  看来没有生命危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.19,0:12:52.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}到底发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:55.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她要从这里到天上去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:06.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.57,0:13:13.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎么了  往人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.51,0:13:15.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不知为什么  心境很乱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:18.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好像很熟悉  又好像很悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.16,0:13:22.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}让佳乃躺下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:33.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}国崎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.71,0:13:47.26,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我的名字叫白穗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:50.40,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}无论如何请听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:56.29,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我记得那时的秋天是很美丽的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:14:00.41,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}他是我们夫妇的第一个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.06,0:14:04.58,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在他的右手腕有一块天生的痣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.39,0:14:07.27,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}村民们都说这不吉利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.73,0:14:09.80,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但我们却并没有在意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:12.85,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}八云哭闹起来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:16.52,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我便会将母亲教给我的摇篮曲唱给他听
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.80,0:14:21.66,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}听到这个八云便会平静下来  但只有这一天不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.07,0:14:38.39,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我本想  这根羽毛一定是神赐给我们的护身符
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:53.96,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}带走！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:55.65,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}战争开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.03,0:14:59.14,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我的丈夫再也没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:11.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这个村子里有没有人捡到了发光的羽毛？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:14.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}羽毛是邪恶的东西  碰过那个的人都给我站出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:19.15,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我趁着那个夜晚逃了出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:37.45,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就这样  我来到了这个村子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.18,0:15:46.26,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神社的宫司热心收留了我们母子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:50.48,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我本以为在这个安宁的小村子里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.89,0:15:54.47,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我可以和八云一起开始新的生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.41,0:15:58.67,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可是  在那一年的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.03,0:16:00.83,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}村子里流行起了瘟疫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:03.07,AIR context 5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}很多人死去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.85,0:16:07.85,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}宫司先生  这孩子怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.64,0:16:09.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}已经渡过危险期了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:11.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}天亮后烧也就会退了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.71,0:16:17.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可是  村民们认为是你们母子带来的瘟疫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:18.60,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:23.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我不该让你们住到这里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:26.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这里祭奠着「巫女神」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.82,0:16:30.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}「巫女神」会给为这片土地带来灾难的人刻上烙印
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:33.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}如果知道这孩子有痣的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:36.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}他们一定会逼着你将孩子献给神的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.54,0:16:41.06,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}难道要将这孩子作为活祭品吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:44.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这片土地就是这样平静灾祸的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.89,0:16:49.84,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这孩子是我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:53.33,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是丈夫留给我的唯一的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.79,0:16:54.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你还是放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.19,0:16:57.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不然连你也会被杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.30,0:17:02.97,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那么  还不如我亲手…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:19.04,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:20.92,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.86,0:17:24.19,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}世上怎么会有杀死自己孩子的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:26.37,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就算是自己的孩子会使世界毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:28.99,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也不会有杀死自己孩子的母亲的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:32.83,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}让我来… 代替他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:34.62,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}请无论如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:37.33,AIR context 3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}救救这个孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:41.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}别做傻事！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.52,0:17:57.20,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:02.02,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}妈妈你在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.67,0:18:03.69,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.01,0:18:09.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:13.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有什么想吃的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.50,0:18:15.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}已经吃过很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:16.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有想要的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:18.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:23.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:26.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因为姐姐在等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:28.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}还有土豆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:32.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}和我的新朋友们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.81,0:18:33.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:37.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}他说他在找天空中的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:41.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我也想过如果自己是那个少女就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:44.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}如果悲伤的话  就同我一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.87,0:18:50.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那个… 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:52.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:56.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}虽然我已经记不清妈妈了
